ActIndian Act
SubjectBrokenhead Indian Reserve No. 4, Na-sha-ke-penais Indian Reserve, and Birch Landing Indian Reserve (Manitoba) ** Designation for leasing purposes **
PrecisOrder accepting a DESIGNATION for leasing purposes of approximately 313.55 hectares (774.78 acres) of land on a portion of BROKENHEAD INDIAN RESERVE No. 4, the whole of NA-SHA-KE-PENAIS INDIAN RESERVE, and the whole of BIRCH LANDING INDIAN RESERVE, in Manitoba.
